<!DOCTYPE html>
<html t:type="Layout" title="About Application"
      xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_4.xsd"
      xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter">

<h3>Goals</h3>
<p class="well">
 Help to create a secured Tapestry application with easily customisable layout<br/>
 Provide configurable tools to manage UI page links, icons in the navbar and <a href="http://www.getbootstrap.com">Bootstrap</a> themes (Bootswatch) activation<br/><br/>
 User Access Control per page should be configurable with Tynamo Tapestry Security/Apache Shiro Page @Annotations authorizations, via an UI (like with Apache Syncope).<br/>
 Serve as a basis to generate a full Tapestry application with MinuteProject (already available to generate JPA, like Apache OpenJPA generator)(like Apache ISIS).
</p>
</html>
